Package an Einstein Bot Template

To create a managed package and share your bot templates between orgs or on AppExchange:

* Einstein Bots is available in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
* You need Customize Application, Modify Metadata, or Manage Bots permissions to build and manage Einstein Bots.

Create a first- or second-generation managed package. To choose the right approach, see Comparison of First- and Second-Generation Managed Packages.

To create a first-generation package:

* See Create a Package in the First-Generation Managed Packaging Developer Guide.
* Choose a packaging type.
* Add your bot template.
* Include variables, entities, Flows, or custom Apex code if necessary.

If creating a second-generation package, see Before You Create a Second-Generation Managed Package in the Second-Generation Managed Packaging Developer Guide.
title: Package an Einstein Bot Template in Service Cloud
